DESCRIPTION:Saturday May 9\, 2026\, 10:30am-12:45pm. Arrive by 10am. Park at Roberts Regional ($5)\, walk back out of the lot\, turn right onto Skyline Blvd for 500 feet\, cross the street and follow the trail. Attire: Redwood Torah casual.\n\nIf you get lost\, look for ~200 Jews wandering in the forest.\n\nKiddush lunch (bagels & lox) follows at ~12:30pm.\n\nCell reception may be limited in the redwoods. Day-of on-call: Gabi 510-207-3137.\n\nFull details: https://benjaminste.in/zekes-bar-mitzvah/
URL:https://benjaminste.in/zekes-bar-mitzvah/
STATUS:CONFIRMED
TRANSP:OPAQUE
END:VEVENT
